data.title: Snoop Dogg - Social Deviance
data.meta_description: Snoop Dogg - Social Deviance - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Snoop Dogg grew up in a crime-ridden neighborhood and was involved in gang and drug activity. He was discovered for his rap music in the early 1990s and found great success, despite the odds against him. Throughout his career, Snoop has experimented with different music genres and collaborated with various artists. He has also given back to his community through charitable causes and mentoring at-risk youth to help keep them away from gangs and crime.
